             re-examined. The prisoner returned the day he took these things home; he did not tell me he had been Mr. Jones afterwards - I had no opportunity of settling with the prisoner when he left; he went to dinner one day, and did not return: I think that was in February</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 58.</p>
